\begin_layout Definition
Метрика, заданная на 
\begin_inset Formula $X$
\end_inset

 — функция 
\begin_inset Formula $\rho:X\times X\to\mathbb{R}$
\end_inset

, такая, что:
\end_layout

\begin_layout Definition
1) 
\begin_inset Formula $\rho(x,y)=0\Leftrightarrow x=y$
\end_inset

;
\end_layout

\begin_layout Definition
2) 
\begin_inset Formula $\rho(x,y)\geq0\ \forall x,y$
\end_inset

;
\end_layout

\begin_layout Definition
3) 
\begin_inset Formula $\rho(x,y)=\rho(y,x)$
\end_inset

;
\end_layout

\begin_layout Definition
4) 
